- **Text**: ![#270185](https://via.placeholder.com/15/270185/270185.png) `#270185`

### Suggestions for Usage
- Combine the **primary** and **secondary** colors for a sleek, modern look.
- Use the **accent** color sparingly to maintain balance and direct attention.
- Pair the **text** color with the **background** for readability.
- Use **highlight** color only for critical elements.